title: Metabolic rewiring in psoriatic keratinocytes by Hsa-miR-31-5p identifies therapeutic intervention
description: Source microscopy images of article that submitted to EMBO molecular medicine with title of "Metabolic rewiring in psoriatic keratinocytes by Hsa-miR-31-5p identifies therapeutic intervention". This paper illustrate an emerging concept of metabolic interaction across cell compartments that characterizes disease development, which can be employed to design effective treatment options for disease, as shown here for psoriasis.
